    "role": "Pipeline stage task that constructs a knowledge graph from the module dependency graph, runs structural diagnostics (cycle detection, dead code detection, hub detection), and persists views (JSON outputs) and health flags for downstream inspection.",
    "responsibilities": [
      "Build a dependency graph for tracked files using the buildGraph engine.",
      "Run diagnostics: detect cycles, detect dead code (modules with no dependents), detect hubs (highly depended-upon modules).",
      "Save views of the graph and each diagnostic result to the output manager.",
      "Write health flags (e.g., hasCycles, hasDeadCode, hasHubs) to the output for fast status checks.",
      "Read the index document from the file system to determine root nodes for graph construction.",
      "Register as a SpineTask with name 'Knowledge Graph Construction' and checkpointId 'knowledge-graph'."
